<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-4188] NoSuchFieldError when defining a field named &quot;metaClass&quot;</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-4188</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The following script causes a NoSuchFieldError. It would be better if all Groovy-internal members started with &quot;$&quot;, or at least caused a sensible compile error.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;Foo {
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;private&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; metaClass
}
  
  
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Foo()
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12815150">GROOVY-4188</key>
